<h2 class="bold font-l">Business Cards</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Yuppies at Pierce &amp; Pierce are all impressed by the minor differences in their near-identical business cards. When Patrick Bateman - a psychopath with a fragile ego - sees Paul Allen's card, he treats it like its the end of the world. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SeriousBusiness" class='trope-example-link'>Serious Business</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="a08ka5" data-video-descrip="Patrick showcases how deranged and psychopathic he is by talking nonsense about bands and then brutally butchering Paul Allen with an axe." data-video-title="Patrick Bateman" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/a08ka5_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/a08ka5.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/AxCrazy" data-video-tropename="Ax-Crazy" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Literature/AmericanPsycho,Film/AmericanPsycho" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/a08ka5.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Patrick Bateman</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="z7ka6j" data-video-descrip="Patrick Bateman, the titular &amp;quot;American Psycho&amp;quot;, is a rich yuppie and a complete psychopath. " data-video-title="Patrick Bateman" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/z7ka6j_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/z7ka6j.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/SerialKiller" data-video-tropename="Serial Killer" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Literature/AmericanPsycho" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/z7ka6j.jpg">
